  "carsP2": (()=>{const fn=(ctx) => {const { normalize: _normalize } = ctx;return _normalize(["Visit Heydar Aliyev Center. The Heydar Aliyev Center is a cultural center, which is a complex construction that includes an auditorium (congress center), a museum, exhibition halls, administrative offices. The project of the Center was designed by famous architect Zaha Hadid. The Center regularly holds exhibitions of paintings by famous artists, art figures. Here y ou can see both temporary and permanent expositions. One of the permanent exhibitions in the museum is an exhibition of classic cars, which we will stop at today. This collection represents cars produced from the beginning of the moment of the emergence of automobile production - from the end of the 19th century. During the excursion tourists will learn interesting facts about the development of the auto industry, the history of the creation of vehicles and, of course, will see rare models of cars of both European and Soviet production."])};fn.source="Visit Heydar Aliyev Center. The Heydar Aliyev Center is a cultural center, which is a complex construction that includes an auditorium (congress center), a museum, exhibition halls, administrative offices. The project of the Center was designed by famous architect Zaha Hadid. The Center regularly holds exhibitions of paintings by famous artists, art figures. Here y ou can see both temporary and permanent expositions. One of the permanent exhibitions in the museum is an exhibition of classic cars, which we will stop at today. This collection represents cars produced from the beginning of the moment of the emergence of automobile production - from the end of the 19th century. During the excursion tourists will learn interesting facts about the development of the auto industry, the history of the creation of vehicles and, of course, will see rare models of cars of both European and Soviet production.";return fn;})(),
